item.title: This Month in German, Swiss, and Austrian (GSA) Startups - March 2024
item.description: Welcome to our March 2024 wrap-up with vital news from the startup and tech entrepreneurship scenes in Germany, Austria, and Switzerland in 30 minutes or less ????. Our startup news is recorded with Chris in New York City and Joe in Frankfurt. Recording date is March 25th 2024 and all news not included will be in our next news to be released on April 25th 2024. Happy Easter!Today we publish on Holy Thursday (Gründonnerstag) in Germany... Feed: https://fintechgermany.podcaster.de/fintechgermany.rss
